info.summary: GPT Cache, make your chatgpt services lower cost and faster

info.author: SimFG
info.name: gptcache
info.summary: GPTCache, a powerful caching library that can be used to speed up and lower the cost of chat applications that rely on the LLM service. GPTCache works as a memcache for AIGC applications, similar to how Redis works for traditional applications.
